            <p>Lysistrate: Panathenais</p></div>

            <div type="commentary">
            <p>Lysistrate is the name of the deidcatee. Panathenais is perahps a name of a second
                    dedicatee who had died shortly after Lysistrate and her name was added (adding
                    name to an existing grave stela was customary). The museum labal gives the more
                    accurate dating 350-325 BCE. </p></div>
            
